   - Shield taken.  
   - Note read.  
   - Railcar examined.  
   - Railcar door opened.  
   - Power button pressed (yellow/green/red).  
   - (Any new items acquired.)  
   Update the list after each successful action.

6. **If stuck** (no new score for 5 consecutive turns):  
